# ESP32 Universal Smart Remote

## Overview

A WiFi-enabled universal remote built using ESP32-S3.

Features:

- Learn IR codes
- Store codes in flash
- Send IR commands
- Web dashboard
- Control appliances from phone

## Hardware

- ESP32-S3
- IR Receiver
- IR LED

